#Grazed sites
# tests of canonical dimensions
ev <- (1 - cc1G$cor^2)

n <- dim(fruG)[1]
p <- length(fruG)
q <- length(plantG)
k <- min(p, q)
m <- n - 3/2 - (p + q)/2

w <- rev(cumprod(rev(ev)))

# initialize
d1 <- d2 <- f <- vector("numeric", k)

for (i in 1:k) {
    s <- sqrt((p^2 * q^2 - 4)/(p^2 + q^2 - 5))
    si <- 1/s
    d1[i] <- p * q
    d2[i] <- m * s - p * q/2 + 1
    r <- (1 - w[i]^si)/w[i]^si
    f[i] <- r * d2[i]/d1[i]
    p <- p - 1
    q <- q - 1
}

pv <- pf(f, d1, d2, lower.tail = FALSE)

#Ungrazed sites
# tests of canonical dimensions
ev <- (1 - cc1UG$cor^2)

n <- dim(fruUG)[1]
p <- length(fruUG)
q <- length(plantUG)
k <- min(p, q)
m <- n - 3/2 - (p + q)/2

w <- rev(cumprod(rev(ev)))

# initialize
d1 <- d2 <- f <- vector("numeric", k)

for (i in 1:k) {
    s <- sqrt((p^2 * q^2 - 4)/(p^2 + q^2 - 5))
    si <- 1/s
    d1[i] <- p * q
    d2[i] <- m * s - p * q/2 + 1
    r <- (1 - w[i]^si)/w[i]^si
    f[i] <- r * d2[i]/d1[i]
    p <- p - 1
    q <- q - 1
}

pv <- pf(f, d1, d2, lower.tail = FALSE)
(dmat <- cbind(WilksL = w, F = f, df1 = d1, df2 = d2, p = pv))
